tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE video_playback_data (
  viewer_id INT,
  video_id INT,
  playback_timestamp TIMESTAMP,
  playback_duration INT,
  playback_speed FLOAT
)

CREATE TABLE playback_data (
  user_id INT,
  video_id INT,
  playback_timestamp TIMESTAMPTZ,
  playback_duration INTERVAL,
  playback_speed DECIMAL
);

CREATE TABLE video_metadata (
  video_id INT,
  video_title VARCHAR(255),
  video_duration INTERVAL,
  video_resolution VARCHAR(10),
  video_format VARCHAR(10)
);

CREATE TABLE playback_data (
    playback_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    video_id UUID REFERENCES video_metadata(video_id),
    user_id UUID,
    playback_start TIMESTAMP,
    playback_end TIMESTAMP,
    playback_duration INT
);

CREATE TABLE playback_data (
    video_id UUID,
    user_id UUID,
    playback_start_time TIMESTAMPTZ,
    playback_end_time TIMESTAMPTZ,
    playback_duration INTERVAL,
    playback_quality TEXT
);

CREATE TABLE video_metadata (
    video_id UUID,
    video_title TEXT,
    upload_time TIMESTAMPTZ,
    video_duration INTERVAL,
    video_resolution TEXT
);

CREATE TABLE user_profile (
    user_id UUID,
    user_name TEXT,
    country_code TEXT,
    account_created_date DATE,
    last_login_time TIMESTAMPTZ
);

CREATE TABLE playback_errors (
    error_id UUID,
    video_id UUID,
    user_id UUID,
    error_description TEXT,
    error_time TIMESTAMPTZ
);

CREATE TABLE VideoCatalog (
    video_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    video_title VARCHAR(255),
    category VARCHAR(50),
    duration_minutes INT
)

CREATE TABLE PlaybackLog (
    log_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    video_id INT,
    playback_timestamp TIMESTAMP,
    viewer_id INT,
    playback_duration_seconds INT
)

CREATE TABLE ViewerProfile (
    viewer_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    viewer_name VARCHAR(100),
    country VARCHAR(50),
    age INT
)

CREATE TABLE VideoQuality (
    video_id INT,
    playback_timestamp TIMESTAMP,
    resolution_height INT,
    resolution_width INT,
    average_bitrate INT
)

CREATE TABLE ErrorLog (
    error_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    log_id INT,
    error_type VARCHAR(50),
    error_description TEXT
)
